title: Hard.Enduro.Auckland.City.Scramble.2012.FUEL.720P.h264.English
description:
We look forward to some of the roughest, toughest races of the year including The Tough One, Hell's Gate, Erzberg Rodeo, Red Bull Romaniacs and Red Bull Sea to Sky. Featuring Graham Jarvis, Jonny Walker, Dougie Lampkin and a host of top riders.

Hundreds of tonnes of rocks, dirt, logs, concrete and tyres are used to transform the idyllic setting of T-Pier in NZ Aucklands Westhaven into an Enduro-cross track of epic proportions. Over 10,000 spectators watch 80 riders battle it out for the City Scramble title.
